fields.name: Seven-Minute Workout
fields.description: Work all of your main muscle groups with this short routine which can be done at home. Do each of these exercises for 30-45 seconds and finish with a few stretches if time permits.

fields.name: Advanced Seven-Minute Workout
fields.description: Work your main muscle groups with this more challenging seven-minute home workout. Do each of these exercises for 30-45 seconds and finish with a few stretches if time permits.
fields.B: - Reverse lunge with elbow to instep

fields.name: Ten-Minute Cardio Workout
fields.description: Get your heart rate up with a quick at-home cardio workout. Do each of these exercises for about 60 seconds and finish with a few stretches if time permits.
fields.E: - Run in place with butt kicks
fields.G: - Run in place with high knees

fields.name: Eight-Minute Yoga Workout
fields.description: Relax and challenge your muscles with this at-home yoga routine (requires prior knowledge of yoga). Hold each of these poses for 30-45 seconds.
